</ul>
<p><strong>Figure 3-2</strong> Suzhou University Parent Occupation over time, 1949-2002
(see chart in PDF manuscript)</p>
<ul>
<li>grey, at least one of the parent has entered occupation</li>
<li>red, professionals</li>
<li>purple, business services personnel</li>
<li>orange, manufacturing, transportation personnel</li>
